"原生引擎純 Apple 框架、不依賴外部核心，支援 SS / Trojan / VLESS / SOCKS5（含 ws/wss），並支援 REALITY、XTLS Vision 與自建 TLS 1.3 偽裝瀏覽器指紋；尚不支援 Hysteria2 / TUIC / VMess / TUN——這些請改用 sing-box 引擎。" = "The native engine uses pure Apple frameworks with no external core. Supports SS / Trojan / VLESS / SOCKS5 (incl. ws/wss), plus REALITY, XTLS Vision, and a built-in TLS 1.3 browser-fingerprint disguise; Hysteria2 / TUIC / VMess / TUN are not yet supported — use the sing-box engine for those.";
